                                    </div><div id="weixin_content"><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.15625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvlZQbgpxXsriaictvBc0ztbZoyPq2cUwnvD7RGJ8QiahiaLOzj3Pu1rAWFRGHhyJT6yGWykOogKxOXpog/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section class="_editor" style="max-width: 100%;text-align: center;"><section data-width="100%" style="padding: 10px;max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;width: 466.364px;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;max-width: 100%;text-align: justify;font-size:15px;line-height:35px;;line-height: 1.8;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">1999年7月2日，一位帅气的苏州小伙走进了园区安德鲁电信器材公司（现更名为康普通讯技术（中国）有限公司）的大门。这位小伙就是现在被同事亲切称为“任大师”的任唯明。</span></p></section></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-bottom: -5px;max-width: 100%;text-align: right;line-height: 1;font-size:6px;line-height:26px;;transform: translate3d(5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;width: 0px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;border-bottom: 0.6em solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-right: 0.6em solid rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border-top: 0.6em solid transparent !important;border-left: 0.6em solid transparent !important;"></section></section></section></section><p><br  /></p></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">这位小伙</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">就是现在被同事亲切称为</span></strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">“任大师”的任唯明</span></strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><section class="KolEditor" data-tools-id="47617" style="max-width: 100%;overflow: hidden;"><section style="margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;padding: 20px;max-width: 100%;background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmDLCtCCNlSCTibZpqtFbBrMIa3CqiaAmVZx0jaiaNA1MsCbG7ffC1UaUHbYyU33P62aLLSPmJQCS6xg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);background-size: cover;background-position: 0% 50%;background-repeat: no-repeat;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding: 5px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: pre-wrap;text-align: justify;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">近20年过去了，原先的年轻人现在已被岁月磨炼成一位年过半百，却依旧风度翩翩的长者。这些年，任唯明见证了公司从二三百人成长为近四千人的团队规模，见证了园区从一片稻田发展成为一座现代新城，更重要的是，他也见证了自己从一位普通技术工人，一路执着深耕，成长为在数控机床领域中发挥重要价值的“技术大师”。</span></p></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.6670378619153675" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmDLCtCCNlSCTibZpqtFbBrMqJo573H1UUccyoyxyH2PlcsGsFyg2tg48iaSu2UPAWSwkbklQcaxCYw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="898" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><section class="KolEditor" style="max-width: 100%;overflow: hidden;"><section class="" style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.12362637362637363" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmDLCtCCNlSCTibZpqtFbBrM6Pg5enBz70dwG448mq1Dyu9wjbNNXNCRlDicVf5B22TsLiapMRZKlIKg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="728" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">1983年，任唯明毕业后被正式分配到苏州第二纺织厂铸工车间维修组。由于是铸工车间的唯一车工，独立完成车间生产计划和加工工艺的制定，很快，他就成为一个优秀的车工。随着生产科技的发展，到1996年，二纺机也有了数控车床，引进的是美国哈铤公司先进的数控机床。由于任唯明是厂里的操作能手，有一定的理论基础，厂领导点名要他去负责操作数控机床，并带领几名工人一起将4台数控车床投入生产，大量的编程工作和特殊的技术要求，使任唯明的编程技术得到了锻炼和提高。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">1999年，机缘巧合下，任唯明进入园区安德鲁电信器材公司，虽然此时已经积累不少的工作经验&nbsp;他仍然不断学习先进的机械加工设备，在实践中提升自身技能，并多次参与解决企业生产技术难题。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.7839506172839507" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmDLCtCCNlSCTibZpqtFbBrMriaYIEZ6E0LjH8DezkeOuPdiaR0woEVTxeoFrAiacRjTqKDGkZ7RaxIUQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="648" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">2010年，任唯明带领团队完成GB501项目，把车床加工的零件转移到铣削中心加工，提高了铣削加工中心的机床利用率，同时解放了6轴车床的产能，彻底解决了供应链问题。这个项目也让他和团队获得安德鲁公司总部颁发的年度项目铜奖。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">2016年，公司需要生产一款用于支持未来5G网络的重要零件（FPA），这款产品在欧洲市场由于加工工艺难度而受阻，研发总部到达国内寻找合作加工。任唯明在分析产品加工特性和加工要求后发现薄板零件加工难点是：不能变形，150mm的范围平面度不允许超出0.1mm，加工256个微小型腔和相关线连接处不允许有毛刺，不允许倒角。结合丰富的加工经验和理论基础，任唯明和他的团队确定必须利用真空夹具才能完美完成这个重要零件的加工。由于当时公司内没有使用过真空夹具，他就带领技术员到五金市场去调研，了解气动工具的配件，向老板们了解气动工具的性能，特性及如何正确使用。功夫不负有心人，最后，他和团队终于设计出符合产品要求的夹具，值得一提的是，所用真空夹具多是内部员工自己制造，投入成本也是极低。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">……</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">一系列的“成绩”让公司称赞不已</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">但任唯明并没有居功自满</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">而是开启了自己的另一扇“大门”</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><section class="KolEditor" style="max-width: 100%;overflow: hidden;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.12362637362637363" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmDLCtCCNlSCTibZpqtFbBrMNFMSp6zrGe9CEOkX2JX58yKBRgcjaAHnb3GzQlDJef3gucgic7XcUyA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="728" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">50岁的任唯明一开始也没想到，从一名普通技术工人成长为高级技师、高级工程师，还有机会成立以他名字命名的大师工作室。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">事实上，在自己申报成立技能大师工作室之前，任唯明就已先后参加了“苏州数控大师工作室”和“胡国强大师工作室”，同时他还是苏州技师协会理事，对苏州地区的数控技术传授和培养起了积极作用。“参加名师工作室，收获很多，包括深入的意志、学习的激情、团队和跨行业交流的活力。”任唯明说。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.6455172413793103" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmDLCtCCNlSCTibZpqtFbBrMqt2RibITaFCVD1J5hLwyxMYpSYOTXRJhKBmaAEqjX8TErfY27ZItn6w/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="725" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">也许正是有了这些经历，当机会来临的时候，他选择一把抓住。2015年，在任唯明的积极申报和推动下，康普通讯技术（中国）有限公司的多轴数控机床技能大师工作室获批为苏州市大师工作室，他担任带头人。对于这个新平台，他相信，也自信能够发挥好带头人作用，加快技术创新，培养更多高技能人才。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">如今，工作室除任唯明之外，还有10多位成员，都具备技师、高级工职称，部分成员还是园区领军人才和姑苏重点人才。大家平时会聚在一起研究技术改造提升，同时，工作室还通过开展各类活动促进团队成员成长，并辐射带动公司其他员工和外围工人技能素质提升。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><section class="KolEditor" style="max-width: 100%;overflow: hidden;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.12362637362637363" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmDLCtCCNlSCTibZpqtFbBrMvEnkbYaYGvaeVPm2Ilnorzn7eibIWdjvDnNZyoYicicJOdZ5njPmNERaw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="728" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><section class="KolEditor" style="max-width: 100%;overflow: hidden;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.5555555555555556" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmDLCtCCNlSCTibZpqtFbBrMicVQic66fyxlAbng0tPzawjzhxa8zU5zJYXfvAQaBZiakia8PJpGFXBHLg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">台面之下的他，是一个乐于分享和传授经验的“技术输出导师”。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.6626106194690266" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmDLCtCCNlSCTibZpqtFbBrMQc8HwuynhwZAmxI9qMARMtiaLar2icA3IbkM07kTlicxk3aQVfbDqsibag/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="904" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">工作中，任唯明带领员工一起积极学习新技术，新知识，他经常组织大家进行技术演讲和技术交流，鼓励员工独立负责完成改善项目，有机会也送他们外出学习和培训。从2005年园区的第一届高技能人才大赛开始，任唯明基本每次都带队参加，提高了公司员工的技能，拓宽了眼界，也看到了差距，培养了一批批优秀的技术人才。目前公司有百余位员工考取了苏州劳动局颁发的各类高级技工证，技师等。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">他的同事毕道来说：“这些年，任大师带领我们参加了很多场技能资格认证的考核。在考核前他不仅自己给我们做培训，还邀请了外面的专家来做分享。大家不仅技术学到了，还拿到了国家的认可证书，对自己的发展有很大帮助。一些在考核中非常优秀的同事甚至还拿到了政府的补贴，给大家带来了实实在在的实惠。我们都非常尊重和感谢他。”</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">现在，任唯明又多了重“导师”的身份，兼任苏州技师学院教学咨询官、园区职业技术学院兼职副教授、苏州工业园区工业自动化公共实训基地首席技能大师等职务。在数控技术输出的道路上，在实现自我价值的道路上，他正不遗余力地走下去。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">其实像任唯明这样的员工在康普通讯还有很多，他们都是从一个个普通的员工开始，从基层岗位做起，得益于苏州以及园区高技能人才培养体制建设，借助于公司的人才培养机制，不断学习和积累，成为了公司的技术骨干。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">康普通讯的人才发展战略是怎样的？</span></strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">快跟着先锋君一起来了解下</span></span></strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">康普通讯技术（中国）有限公司是美国康普公司的子公司。工厂位于苏州工业园苏虹西路68号。公司成立于1997年，现有员工超过3,500人。工厂生产基站天线、射频同轴电缆、接头、电缆组件和滤波器等有线和无线网络基础架构产品。除生产运营团队外，苏州工厂还设有康普集团最大规模的研发中心，为全球客户提供前沿的设计服务，同时拥有客户服务，技术服务中心，为客户提供专业的售前售后服务。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><section class="_editor" style="max-width: 100%;"></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: pre-wrap;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><section class="_editor" style="max-width: 100%;"><section data-width="100%" style="max-width: 100%;width: 466.364px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="100%" style="max-width: 100%;width: 466.364px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.4285714285714286" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Ljib4So7yuWhz0ox2DdB6YNo41u9lDKNnf5P22SSdaIv6CUIRBIkZ2R3GJ6RScDptnQkuw3ATUwqygAWlRzFF1A/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="175" style="vertical-align: middle;width: 20px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="max-width: 100%;font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">建立结构化的全面人才发展解决方案</section></section></section><section class="_editor" style="max-width: 100%;"><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: pre-wrap;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">在康普全球人才战略和政府的各项发展人才的激励政策下，康普苏州经过多年的运营，已经形成了完善的为各层次员工提供的人才发展解决方案。它既包括保证生产运营的一线工人的技能发展体系，也包括公司的年度菜单式培训，涵盖通用、专业知识、LEAN、EAP、领导力等体系。员工可以年初在线上根据自己的业务需求和个人发展需要选择自己要参加的培训内容。同时公司根据业务战略重点，发展一些关键人才的发展项目。如GOLD（全球生产一线主管/领班发展项目）、EDP（工程技术人员发展项目）、MDP和LEAP（经理发展项目）。每一个项目都根据这些关键人才的特点量身定制各种能力提高、业务发展以及实践运用的学习内容。完善的、结构化的人才发展体系为公司的各项业务重点提供了人才的保证。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><section class="_editor" style="max-width: 100%;"><section data-width="100%" style="max-width: 100%;width: 466.364px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="100%" style="max-width: 100%;width: 466.364px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.4285714285714286" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Ljib4So7yuWhz0ox2DdB6YNo41u9lDKNn3piav5jhRVt4UBUd11icFkvG0QISvDRibsXV8tOFhSYFgdNWibZjjutzwg/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="175" style="vertical-align: middle;width: 20px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="max-width: 100%;font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">搭建实践学习协会，学用互促</section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: pre-wrap;"><br  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">为了实现让培训效果落地，切实提升员工的绩效这一目标，公司在培训过程中会使用行为学习法、培训后测验、实践分享等各种形式促进员工学以致用。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">同时公司从2012年开始搭建PLS（Practice Learning Sharing）实践学习分享平台。这个平台下辖三个协会：内训师协会、领班协会、工程技术协会，每个协会经过六年的初创、成长、成熟，已经成为陪伴员工在工作之外最喜爱的学习成长的重要平台，在这里倾诉自己的工作难点，分享自己和学习别人的工作经验，认识对自己很有帮助的朋友，学习行业新技术，开拓自己的眼界。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><section class="_editor" data-color="rgb(89, 195, 249)" style="max-width: 100%;text-align: center;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;z-index: 9999;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding-right: 1em;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 1em;max-width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(63, 63, 63);background: rgb(89, 195, 249);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;">内训师协会</span></section></section></section><section style="margin-top: 4px;max-width: 100%;width: 3px;background: rgb(89, 195, 249);border-right: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-top: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section><section style="margin-left: 4px;max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="100%" style="max-width: 100%;width: 110.994px;height: 4px;background: rgb(89, 195, 249);border-right: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-left: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-top: none;z-index: 9999;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: pre-wrap;"><br  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">公司的学习体系、学习项目的课程大多由内训师团队完成，公司共拥有近100位内训师。内训师协会致力于帮助内训师不断提高课程开发能力、授课技巧、逻辑思维、运用微课技术等能力。为内训师保持高昂的热情同时输出高质量的课程保驾护航。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><section class="_editor" data-color="rgb(89, 195, 249)" style="max-width: 100%;text-align: center;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;z-index: 9999;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding-right: 1em;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 1em;max-width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(63, 63, 63);background: rgb(89, 195, 249);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">领班协会</section></section></section><section style="margin-top: 4px;max-width: 100%;width: 3px;background: rgb(89, 195, 249);border-right: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-top: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section><section style="margin-left: 4px;max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="100%" style="max-width: 100%;width: 106.278px;height: 4px;background: rgb(89, 195, 249);border-right: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-left: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-top: none;z-index: 9999;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: pre-wrap;"><br  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">苏州工厂是康普全球的重要生产基地，而领班这个群体是保证生产的各项目标完成的重要一线管理团队。领班协会多种多样的活动形式，不仅能让领班在这个平台上找到共同的心声，学习优秀领班的经验，不断提高自己的管理技能，同时还通过各种团队活动结交新朋友，为自己的工作也带来实际的帮助。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><section class="_editor" data-color="rgb(89, 195, 249)" style="max-width: 100%;text-align: center;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;z-index: 9999;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding-right: 1em;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 1em;max-width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(63, 63, 63);background: rgb(89, 195, 249);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;">工程技术协会</span></section></section></section><section style="margin-top: 4px;max-width: 100%;width: 3px;background: rgb(89, 195, 249);border-right: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-top: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section><section style="margin-left: 4px;max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="100%" style="max-width: 100%;width: 126.634px;height: 4px;background: rgb(89, 195, 249);border-right: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-left: 1px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);border-top: none;z-index: 9999;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"  /></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">工程技术协会发展到今年，已经呈现出百花齐放的姿态。协会成立了各种跨部门分享平台，如自动化、产品和市场、测试、质量、各种重要技术方向的研讨平台。在这些平台上，公司的工程技术人员分享经验，了解这些方向先进的技术，学习创新理念，同时把眼光投向国内、国际的前沿技术，不断提升自己成为一位具有国际竞争力的人才。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.23706896551724138" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvlZQbgpxXsriaictvBc0ztbZoZ0QE5BdJDIoI1JALxdVnjCXfttmIoyE38fNKxwfGZiaJa8j2sslLfMA/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="696" style="box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>
